---
source: crates/wasm-cli/tests/test.rs
expression: output
---
Notify a meta-registry that a new version of a package is available

Usage: wasm registry notify [OPTIONS] <REFERENCE>

Arguments:
  <REFERENCE>  The reference of the newly-published version (e.g., `ghcr.io/example/component:1.2.3`)

Options:
      --registry-url <REGISTRY_URL>
          URL of the meta-registry to notify [default: http://localhost:8080]
  -h, --help
          Print help
  -V, --version
          Print version

Global Options:
      --color <WHEN>  When to use colored output [default: auto] [possible values: auto, always, never]
      --offline       Run in offline mode
  -v, --verbose...    Increase logging verbosity
  -q, --quiet...      Decrease logging verbosity
